&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MUST BE &#39;NMC REGISTERED&#39; TO APPLY&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has come up to work in Bracknell Haemodialysis Unit, this is a 16 bedded satellite unit of the Royal Berkshire Hospital Foundation Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for motivated and highly enthusiastic individuals to become part of our team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidates will undertake a programme of in-house training underpinned by continued support of both personal and professional development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The unit is open Monday to Saturday with no night duty. Informal visits to the unit are highly recommended.&lt;/p&gt;
